{"tid":96711,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個俾廢老批鬥嘅經歷","createTime":"2017-01-27T05:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T06:37:05.000Z","uid":27083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31f08de73efd7b440187d6e09a5d22ab50823c94","tid":96711,"uid":27083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:24:08.000Z","msg":"試過發燒就暈低去搭地鐵<br />\n見到有位就諗住去坐低休息下啦<br />\n點知下一個站有個婆婆上車<br />\n佢企正係我面前<br />\n可能因為成排位入邊我最後生啦<br />\n所以大家都冇讓座<br />\n旨意我讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我又真係好唔舒服喎<br />\n咁我就合埋眼抖下<br />\n點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 婆婆開始俾說話我聽<br />\n話我後生仔唔敬老又話我冇家教<br />\n最嚴重係叫我食屎<br />\n跟住一路鬧到我落車<br />\n利申 最後都冇讓位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fc9c65f7f6a3dce6359eee6510e0e165e18b5b","tid":96711,"uid":14744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:32:37.000Z","msg":"有次搭巴士有兩個批鬥座咁我就坐左路口個個位<br />\n之後有個阿婆同佢個女（40幾歲死肥婆）上車<br />\n之後我讓個阿婆比佢入去坐佢又路坐話我唔讓坐<br />\n屌你老味我都讓開左比你入自己唔撚坐入去關我撚事咩<br />\n仲要大大聲話呢個係關愛座<br />\n我心諗關愛座明明就係冇位座先要讓出黎姐<br />\n點解後面咁多位一定要坐呢個位？<br />\n有位坐仲要我讓出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451f6a004b5c64f3947b4fffddd65ff7c25d1288","tid":96711,"uid":14744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:33:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次搭巴士有兩個批鬥座咁我就坐左路口個個位<br />\n之後有個阿婆同佢個女（40幾歲死肥婆）上車<br />\n之後我讓個阿婆比佢入去坐佢又唔坐話我唔讓坐<br />\n屌你老味我都讓開左比你入自己唔撚坐入去關我撚事咩<br />\n仲要大大聲話呢個係關愛座<br />\n我心諗關愛座明明就係冇位座先要讓出黎姐<br />\n點解後面咁多位一定要坐呢個位？<br />\n有位坐仲要我讓出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"06816cd478d1ac8ef4a5655788efe5e7b51180e3","tid":96711,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:35:12.000Z","msg":"廢青們幾時團結一齊批鬥廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2bace92b1a0692a8b660aea95e8b9dcf5e1880","tid":96711,"uid":5044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:49:23.000Z","msg":"新年願望就係死撚哂去d廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdcde891af5d230d2160206c7c1a9e7ce919280","tid":96711,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢青們幾時團結一齊批鬥廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日仲有偽善撚就一路都會比班廢老得戚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f5b1ffecd05ad00c8f1f03454137138da677cd","tid":96711,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:54:48.000Z","msg":"試過個頭好痛好痛<br />\n坐係近出口，唔係關愛座<br />\n一個阿伯阿婆望實我，個表情係話做乜唔讓比我"},{"pid":"7d15b7d2d673f229bf56f8343dba0c847483108e","tid":96711,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廢青們幾時團結一齊批鬥廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一日仲有偽善撚就一路都會比班廢老得戚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多中年偽善撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 